creator: Fever Labs
descriptionHtml:
Discovering the best events in your city has never been easier!
• Fever creates a curated list of events based on your interests
• Book or buy easily using the app
• Discover which events your friends are going to
• Exclusive access to unique experiences and perks

Fever selects the best events in your city, such as:
• Restaurants (bistros, wine tastings, brunch, Michelin-starred venues, etc.)
• Nightlife (bars, clubs, private parties, after-parties, etc.)
• Concerts (festivals, jam sessions, etc.)
• Cinema and theatre (cinema tickets, previews, film festivals and stand-up comedy, etc.)
• Exhibitions (museums, galleries, art, openings, etc.)
• Fashion (pop-ups, runways, launches, etc.)
• Charity (galas, fundraising, volunteering, etc.)

Available in London, Manchester, Birmingham, USA, Canada, Spain, France, Portugal, Belgium, Brazil and Singapore.

Please note: in order to make the most out of your user experience, you’ll need to log in with Facebook or Google+.

title: Fever: discover local events, book tickets & enjoy

creator: Fever Labs
descriptionHtml:
Fever t’aide à explorer ce qu’il y a à faire dans ta ville, où aller et quoi visiter. Découvre des événements exclusifs, des lieux secrets et des pop-ups branchés où tu pourras vivre de nouvelles expériences. Notre application propose les meilleures offres de loisirs personnalisées.

Disponible à Paris, Lyon, Marseille, Bordeaux, Toulouse, Lille, Nice ...

Principaux avantages et caractéristiques :
👍 Recommandations en fonction de tes centres d’intérêts.
🔎 Recherche ou filtre par catégories pour découvrir les expériences à proximité et les bons plans à venir.
🎫 Enregistre tes événements favoris, paye en deux clics en toute sécurité et récupère tes tickets mobiles.
💬 Assistance 24/7 via chat, téléphone ou email.

Utilise l'application pour réserver et acheter des billets au meilleur prix pour tous les types d'événements.
🍽️ Gastronomie : restaurants, brunchs, cafés, dégustations et dîners
🎭 Théâtre, comédie, cabaret, cirque
🎵 Concerts et festivals
🎧 Soirées
📽️ Films à l’affiche des cinémas Gaumont Pathé et Grand Rex
🏅 Activités sportives
👗 Mode
💆 Bien-être : hammam, spas/massages
👪 Tours, parc d’attraction, activités en groupe
🏛️ Visites culturelles et musées

En savoir plus sur https://feverup.com/
Contacte-nous par mail à salut@feverup.com pour tout problème ou une suggestion.

title: Fever - Découvrir et réserver des événements

creator: Fever Labs
descriptionHtml:
Fever helps you discover what to do in your city, where to go and what to visit. Find exclusive events, secret places, and trendy pop-ups where you can enjoy new experiences. Our app recognizes your tastes and suggests the best personalised leisure offers.

Available in New York City, Boston, Chicago, Denver, Los Angeles, Miami, Seattle, Atlanta, Las Vegas, Austin, Cleveland, Dallas, Detroit, Houston, Minneapolis, New Orleans, Philadelphia, Phoenix, San Diego...

Main benefits and features:

- Personalized recommendations based on your interests.
- Search or filter by topic and you will see nearby experiences and upcoming events.
- Save your favorite plans, pay safely in two clicks and get your mobile tickets.
- 24/7 support via chat, phone or email.

Use the application to book and reserve tickets at the best price for all types of events.

- Food places: restaurants, brunch, gourmet, dining, coffees and food drink fests
- Theater (Broadway), comedy, circus cabaret
- Local gigs, concerts and festivals
- Nightlife, DJ and yacht parties
- AMC movie showtimes
- Sport activities
- Fashion, wellness and spas
- Culture tours, group activities and games

Discover for more at https://feverup.com/
24/7 support via chat, phone or email at hi@feverup.com

title: Fever: discover local events, book tickets & enjoy

creator: Fever Labs
descriptionHtml:
Fever t’aide à explorer ce qu’il y a à faire dans ta ville, où aller et quoi visiter. Découvre des événements exclusifs, des lieux secrets et des pop-ups branchés où tu pourras vivre de nouvelles expériences. Notre application propose les meilleures offres de loisirs personnalisées.

Disponible à Paris, Lyon, Marseille, Bordeaux, Toulouse, Lille, Nice ...

Principaux avantages et caractéristiques :
👍 Recommandations en fonction de tes centres d’intérêts.
🔎 Recherche ou filtre par catégories pour découvrir les expériences à proximité et les bons plans à venir.
🎫 Enregistre tes événements favoris, paye en deux clics en toute sécurité et récupère tes tickets mobiles.
💬 Assistance 24/7 via chat, téléphone ou email.

Utilise l'application pour réserver et acheter des billets au meilleur prix pour tous les types d'événements.
🍽️ Gastronomie : restaurants, brunchs, cafés, dégustations et dîners
🎭 Théâtre, comédie, cabaret, cirque
🎵 Concerts et festivals
🎧 Soirées
📽️ Films à l’affiche des cinémas Gaumont Pathé et Grand Rex
🏅 Activités sportives
👗 Mode
💆 Bien-être : hammam, spas/massages
👪 Tours, parc d’attraction, activités en groupe
🏛️ Visites culturelles et musées

En savoir plus sur https://feverup.com/
Contacte-nous par mail à salut@feverup.com pour tout problème ou une suggestion.

title: Fever: discover local events, book tickets & enjoy

creator: Fever Labs
descriptionHtml:
Fever t’aide à explorer ce qu’il y a à faire dans ta ville, où aller et quoi visiter. Découvre des événements exclusifs, des lieux secrets et des pop-ups branchés où tu pourras vivre de nouvelles expériences. Notre application propose les meilleures offres de loisirs personnalisées.

Disponible à Paris, Lyon, Marseille, Bordeaux, Toulouse, Lille, Nice ...

Principaux avantages et caractéristiques :
👍 Recommandations en fonction de tes centres d’intérêts.
🔎 Recherche ou filtre par catégories pour découvrir les expériences à proximité et les bons plans à venir.
🎫 Enregistre tes événements favoris, paye en deux clics en toute sécurité et récupère tes tickets mobiles.
💬 Assistance 24/7 via chat, téléphone ou email.

Utilise l'application pour réserver et acheter des billets au meilleur prix pour tous les types d'événements.
🍽️ Gastronomie : restaurants, brunchs, cafés, dégustations et dîners
🎭 Théâtre, comédie, cabaret, cirque
🎵 Concerts et festivals
🎧 Soirées
📽️ Films à l’affiche des cinémas Gaumont Pathé et Grand Rex
🏅 Activités sportives
👗 Mode
💆 Bien-être : hammam, spas/massages
👪 Tours, parc d’attraction, activités en groupe
🏛️ Visites culturelles et musées

En savoir plus sur https://feverup.com/
Contacte-nous par mail à salut@feverup.com pour tout problème ou une suggestion.

title: Fever: discover local events, book tickets & enjoy

creator: Fever Labs
descriptionHtml:
Fever t’aide à explorer ce qu’il y a à faire dans ta ville, où aller et quoi visiter. Découvre des événements exclusifs, des lieux secrets et des pop-ups branchés où tu pourras vivre de nouvelles expériences. Notre application propose les meilleures offres de loisirs personnalisées.

Disponible à Paris, Lyon, Marseille, Bordeaux, Toulouse, Lille, Nice ...

Principaux avantages et caractéristiques :
👍 Recommandations en fonction de tes centres d’intérêts.
🔎 Recherche ou filtre par catégories pour découvrir les expériences à proximité et les bons plans à venir.
🎫 Enregistre tes événements favoris, paye en deux clics en toute sécurité et récupère tes tickets mobiles.
💬 Assistance 24/7 via chat, téléphone ou email.

Utilise l'application pour réserver et acheter des billets au meilleur prix pour tous les types d'événements.
🍽️ Gastronomie : restaurants, brunchs, cafés, dégustations et dîners
🎭 Théâtre, comédie, cabaret, cirque
🎵 Concerts et festivals
🎧 Soirées
📽️ Films à l’affiche des cinémas Gaumont Pathé et Grand Rex
🏅 Activités sportives
👗 Mode
💆 Bien-être : hammam, spas/massages
👪 Tours, parc d’attraction, activités en groupe
🏛️ Visites culturelles et musées

En savoir plus sur https://feverup.com/
Contacte-nous par mail à salut@feverup.com pour tout problème ou une suggestion.

title: Fever: Local Events & Tickets

creator: Fever Labs
descriptionHtml:
Fever t’aide à explorer ce qu’il y a à faire dans ta ville, où aller et quoi visiter. Découvre des événements exclusifs, des lieux secrets et des pop-ups branchés où tu pourras vivre de nouvelles expériences. Notre application propose les meilleures offres de loisirs personnalisées.

Disponible à Paris, Lyon, Marseille, Bordeaux, Toulouse, Lille, Nice ...

Principaux avantages et caractéristiques :
👍 Recommandations en fonction de tes centres d’intérêts.
🔎 Recherche ou filtre par catégories pour découvrir les expériences à proximité et les bons plans à venir.
🎫 Enregistre tes événements favoris, paye en deux clics en toute sécurité et récupère tes tickets mobiles.
💬 Assistance 24/7 via chat, téléphone ou email.

Utilise l'application pour réserver et acheter des billets au meilleur prix pour tous les types d'événements.
🍽️ Gastronomie : restaurants, brunchs, cafés, dégustations et dîners
🎭 Théâtre, comédie, cabaret, cirque
🎵 Concerts et festivals
🎧 Soirées
📽️ Films à l’affiche des cinémas Gaumont Pathé et Grand Rex
🏅 Activités sportives
👗 Mode
💆 Bien-être : hammam, spas/massages
👪 Tours, parc d’attraction, activités en groupe
🏛️ Visites culturelles et musées

En savoir plus sur https://feverup.com/
Contacte-nous par mail à salut@feverup.com pour tout problème ou une suggestion.

- Fashion, wellness and spas
- Culture tours, group activities and games

descriptionHtml:

• Fever creates a curated list of events based on your interests
• Book or buy easily using the app
• Discover which events your friends are going to
• Exclusive access to unique experiences and perks

Fever selects the best events in your city, such as:
• Restaurants (bistros, wine tastings, brunch, Michelin-starred venues, etc.)

creator: Fever Labs
descriptionHtml:
Discover the best experiences in your city📍
Fever puts the wealth of your city’s events and experiences at your fingertips. Discover what to do, where to go, and what to visit. Find local events, secret places, and trendy pop-ups, some of which are available exclusively on Fever.

Discover exclusive events that you can only find in Fever:

🦕 Jurassic World: The Exhibition
👾 Stranger Things: The Experience
🎨 Van Gogh: the Immersive Experience
👑The Queens Ball: A Bridgerton Experience
✨ And many more!

Unique Fever features


🎉Exclusive events: Access to exclusive events that you can only find on the Fever platform.
⭐ Fever Club: Reward system on all ticket purchases thanks to your Fever wallet.
⏩ Fever filters: Handy filters that allow you to search by date & time.
❣️ Favorite events: List of favorited experiences for easy access to the events that you like the most.
🎫 Ticket transfers: Easy ticket transfer system that allows you to send friends and family tickets with no fuss.
📍 Map of event locations: Up-to-date map that shows you the events near you and in your city.
🙋 User based recommendations: Personalized recommendations for events and experiences based on your likes.
📱 Fully mobile, paper-free tickets: no printer required as tickets are scanned from your mobile device.
🔧 Customer Support: 24/7 support and chat with our Customer Support team, available in 8 languages.

All types of events and experiences


☛ Tours, trips, adventure: discover new places and experiences in your city that you haven’t even heard of.
☛ Arts & museums: visit your city’s cultural havens for a tranquil day out.
☛ Concerts & festivals: watch your favorite musicians and artists as they perform at some of the most exclusive venues in your city.
☛ Theater, comedy, shows, & AMC cinemas: laugh, cry, sing and shout at the best shows and latest movie screenings.
☛ Food experiences: taste the world at a wide variety of gastronomic experiences.
☛ Drinks & afterwork, nightlife, parties: dance the night away at some of the city’s hottest nighttime spots.
☛ And much more!

Available cities in the US: New York, San Francisco, Los Angeles, Miami, Boston, Chicago, San Diego, Washington DC, Atlanta, Philadelphia, Seattle and many more!

To check out the Fever platform and for any other information, you can take a look at our website https://feverup.com/en or contact us 24/7 support via chat, phone and email at hi@feverup.com.

title:
Fever: Local Events & Tickets
5.112.0

creator: Fever Labs
descriptionHtml:
Discover the best experiences in your city📍
Fever puts the wealth of your city’s events and experiences at your fingertips. Discover what to do, where to go, and what to visit. Find local events, secret places, and trendy pop-ups, some of which are available exclusively on Fever.

Discover exclusive events that you can only find in Fever:

🦕 Jurassic World: The Exhibition
👾 Stranger Things: The Experience
🎨 Van Gogh: the Immersive Experience
👑The Queens Ball: A Bridgerton Experience
✨ And many more!

Unique Fever features


🎉Exclusive events: Access to exclusive events that you can only find on the Fever platform.
⭐ Fever Club: Reward system on all ticket purchases thanks to your Fever wallet.
⏩ Fever filters: Handy filters that allow you to search by date & time.
❣️ Favorite events: List of favorited experiences for easy access to the events that you like the most.
🎫 Ticket transfers: Easy ticket transfer system that allows you to send friends and family tickets with no fuss.
📍 Map of event locations: Up-to-date map that shows you the events near you and in your city.
🙋 User based recommendations: Personalized recommendations for events and experiences based on your likes.
📱 Fully mobile, paper-free tickets: no printer required as tickets are scanned from your mobile device.
🔧 Customer Support: 24/7 support and chat with our Customer Support team, available in 8 languages.

All types of events and experiences


☛ Tours, trips, adventure: discover new places and experiences in your city that you haven’t even heard of.
☛ Arts & museums: visit your city’s cultural havens for a tranquil day out.
☛ Concerts & festivals: watch your favorite musicians and artists as they perform at some of the most exclusive venues in your city.
☛ Theater, comedy, shows, & AMC cinemas: laugh, cry, sing and shout at the best shows and latest movie screenings.
☛ Food experiences: taste the world at a wide variety of gastronomic experiences.
☛ Drinks & afterwork, nightlife, parties: dance the night away at some of the city’s hottest nighttime spots.
☛ And much more!

Available cities in the US: New York, San Francisco, Los Angeles, Miami, Boston, Chicago, San Diego, Washington DC, Atlanta, Philadelphia, Seattle and many more!

To check out the Fever platform and for any other information, you can take a look at our website https://feverup.com/en or contact us 24/7 support via chat, phone and email at hi@feverup.com.

creator: Fever Labs
descriptionHtml:
Discover the best experiences in your city📍

Fever puts the wealth of your city’s events and experiences at your fingertips. Discover what to do, where to go, and what to visit. Find local events, secret places, and trendy pop-ups, some of which are available exclusively on Fever.

Discover exclusive events that you can only find in Fever:

🦕 Jurassic World: The Exhibition
👾 Stranger Things: The Experience
🎨 Van Gogh: the Immersive Experience
👑The Queens Ball: A Bridgerton Experience
✨ And many more!

Unique Fever features


🎉Exclusive events: Access to exclusive events that you can only find on the Fever platform.
⭐ Fever Club: Reward system on all ticket purchases thanks to your Fever wallet.
⏩ Fever filters: Handy filters that allow you to search by date & time.
❣️ Favorite events: List of favorited experiences for easy access to the events that you like the most.
🎫 Ticket transfers: Easy ticket transfer system that allows you to send friends and family tickets with no fuss.
📍 Map of event locations: Up-to-date map that shows you the events near you and in your city.
🙋 User based recommendations: Personalized recommendations for events and experiences based on your likes.
📱 Fully mobile, paper-free tickets: no printer required as tickets are scanned from your mobile device.
🔧 Customer Support: 24/7 support and chat with our Customer Support team, available in 8 languages.

All types of events and experiences


☛ Tours, trips, adventure: discover new places and experiences in your city that you haven’t even heard of.
☛ Arts & museums: visit your city’s cultural havens for a tranquil day out.
☛ Concerts & festivals: watch your favorite musicians and artists as they perform at some of the most exclusive venues in your city.
☛ Theater, comedy, shows, & AMC cinemas: laugh, cry, sing and shout at the best shows and latest movie screenings.
☛ Food experiences: taste the world at a wide variety of gastronomic experiences.
☛ Drinks & afterwork, nightlife, parties: dance the night away at some of the city’s hottest nighttime spots.
☛ And much more!

Available cities in the US: New York, San Francisco, Los Angeles, Miami, Boston, Chicago, San Diego, Washington DC, Atlanta, Philadelphia, Seattle and many more!

To check out the Fever platform and for any other information, you can take a look at our website https://feverup.com/en or contact us 24/7 support via chat, phone and email at hi@feverup.com.

descriptionHtml:
Discovering the best events in your city has never been easier!
• Fever creates a curated list of events based on your interests
• Book or buy easily using the app
• Discover which events your friends are going to
• Exclusive access to unique experiences and perks

Fever selects the best events in your city, such as:
• Restaurants (bistros, wine tastings, brunch, Michelin-starred venues, etc.)
• Nightlife (bars, clubs, private parties, after-parties, etc.)
• Concerts (festivals, jam sessions, etc.)
• Cinema and theatre (cinema tickets, previews, film festivals and stand-up comedy, etc.)
• Exhibitions (museums, galleries, art, openings, etc.)
• Fashion (pop-ups, runways, launches, etc.)
• Charity (galas, fundraising, volunteering, etc.)

Please note: in order to make the most out of your user experience, you’ll need to log in with Facebook or Google+.
